---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Machine Tending — Formic Automate NOW"
  description="Fully managed robotic machine tending — mill, lathe, and injection-mold load/unload under the Formic Full Service model. No CapEx, 24/7 support, one flat monthly rate."
  ogTitle="Robotic Machine Tending — Formic"
  ogDescription="Fully managed mill, lathe, and mold tending. Recover spindle time without staffing it. No CapEx, flat monthly rate."
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/solutions/machine-tending" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/solutions">Solutions</a><span class="sep">/</span>Machine Tending
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Machine Tending</div>
    <h1>Mill, lathe, mold —<br><em>hands-off.</em></h1>
    <p class="lede">Fully managed robotic load and unload for the most repetitive, hardest-to-staff jobs on a precision floor. No CapEx, no new hires — one flat monthly rate, fully supported by Formic.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/MachineTending-CNC.jpg">
        <source src="/Formic-Header.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <span class="dv-cap">Automate NOW · machine tending</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — Automate NOW</div>
      <h2>The fastest way to <em>put a robot on your machine</em>.</h2>
      <p>Most shops lose 20–40% of available spindle time to operator-bound load and unload cycles, breaks, and shift changes. Formic puts a robot on the machines you already run — fully supported under one flat monthly rate — so you get that time back without adding a single shift.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Lights-out third shift on equipment you already own</li>
        <li>24/7 support and 100% maintenance — included</li>
        <li>No CapEx — one flat monthly rate, fully supported</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/#cta" class="larr">Get a quote →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/MachineTending-CNC.jpg" alt="Formic robot tending a CNC machine on a precision floor" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">CNC tending · 24/7 spindle</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/MachineTending-CNC.jpg">
        <source src="/ATLAS_EOAT.webm" type="video/webm" />
      </video>
      <span class="img-cap">Vision pick · part presentation</span>
    </div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — Full Service Automation</div>
      <h2>Vision pick, <em>repeatable place</em>.</h2>
      <p>Vision-guided picking handles part orientation; the robot loads, the machine cycles, the robot unloads, and out-of-spec parts divert at the gauge. Our engineers scope the cell to the machines you already run — and keep it running, every shift.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Compatible with most major CNC, lathe, EDM, and injection-mold platforms</li>
        <li>Multi-machine tending — one robot, two or three spindles</li>
        <li>Inline gauging for in-cell quality verification</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/full-service" class="larr">How Full Service works →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Recover the spindle hours<br><em>you're already paying for.</em></h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get a Quote</a>
    <a href="/solutions" class="btn-ctawh">All Solutions</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
